<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Action Required: License Expiration Warning</h2>
    
    <p>Hello <%= @user&.user_profile&.first_name || "User" %>,</p>
    
    <p>
      This is an automated reminder that your <strong><%= @license&.issuing_authority&.name %></strong> license is set to expire soon.
    </p>

    <h3>License Details</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>License Number:</strong> <%= @license&.license_number %></li>
      <li><strong>Expiration Date:</strong> <%= @license&.expiration_date&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
      <li><strong>Days Remaining:</strong> <%= @days_left %> days</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Please ensure you have completed all required CEU credits before the expiration date to maintain compliance.
    </p>

    <p>
      You can view your current CEU status and update your license details by logging into your dashboard:
    </p>

    <p>
      <%= link_to "Go to Dashboard", dashboard_url %>
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Best regards,<br>
      The App Idea Team
    </p>
  </body>
</html>